{"tid":2179949,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯可自由離隊鐵證曝光！巴塞主席曾親口表態","createTime":"2020-08-29T13:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T15:05:28.000Z","uid":34571,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"aef75ad6e331e49485c87a0887ea5e36f3136cad","tid":2179949,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"美斯（Lionel Messi）想要自由離隊，巴塞高層卻想索要巨額轉會費。美斯的要求有道理嗎？如今媒體翻出了支持美斯主張的一個鐵證。<br />\n<br />\n  阿根廷媒體《奧萊報》表示，巴塞主席貝圖美奧（Josep Bartomeu）曾在2019年的一次採訪中，公開表示美斯可以在今季開始前，自由離隊。該媒體放出了貝圖美奧的這段採訪視頻。<br />\n<br />\n  貝圖美奧當時表示：「美斯和我們有一份兩年前簽訂的合約，為期四年。<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">在2020/21賽季開始之前，他可以自由離開巴塞隆拿。他個人可以在合約到期前離開球隊去自己想去的地方</span></span></strong>，他和沙維（Xavi）、恩尼斯達（Andr&eacute;s Iniesta）、佩奧爾（Carles Puyol）一樣，都熱愛巴塞，他們的合約裡也有著這樣的條款。所以我們不必擔心這個問題，我毫不懷疑他會繼續在巴塞效力，我希望這個時間段是很多年。」<br />\n<br />\n  如今新賽季還未開始，這是否意味著美斯有權自由離開巴塞呢？此前巴塞高層認為，美斯的自由離隊條款在6月就過期了，所以其他隊想要美斯就得支付7億歐元違約金，或者支付高額的轉會費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/08/29/9/920291305f8d24a8b9289d0089b88284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2F9%2F920291305f8d24a8b9289d0089b88284.jpg&h=70177156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/08/29/6/618ff5b37bb6300efbe4dca8af2d06b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2F6%2F618ff5b37bb6300efbe4dca8af2d06b3.jpg&h=a8dc5ce4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04d423efbd1996cca7d723820d1fa12a666d2194","tid":2179949,"uid":71102,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"巴塞高層=中共"},{"pid":"a12a2dd2622fe1c6de4be1a47f931a5ea931e347","tid":2179949,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"bc418bff8da33345837306699fc242f5bceedddc","tid":2179949,"uid":103207,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"巴：對(<span class=\"red\">2020/21賽季開始之前</span>)一詞我巴擁有最終解釋權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e46ded1ff1d13623c70706c7208e324f1aabcf","tid":2179949,"uid":28028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"巴塞有冇基本法?"},{"pid":"75fb14b0859b2bb3715552d90f580818c34be779","tid":2179949,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9e46ded1ff1d13623c70706c7208e324f1aabcf","tid":2179949,"uid":28028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"巴塞有冇基本法?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"樽腐乳呢"},{"pid":"6d459b435d383f5aae277c5f77915c9049ee98ed","tid":2179949,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"我地雄哥話唔得就唔得"},{"pid":"9c3efb49c43fc3f0250ad9e26cd26051454c2547","tid":2179949,"uid":24925,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"錯嘅係疤狗管理層以為美斯會同沙維小白佩奧爾一樣咁忠心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be60d815508a3fd1c3c5216bbe831185433da24c","tid":2179949,"uid":34571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c3efb49c43fc3f0250ad9e26cd26051454c2547","tid":2179949,"uid":24925,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"錯嘅係疤狗管理層以為美斯會同沙維小白佩奧爾一樣咁忠心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:43:09.000Z","msg":"小白沙維都免費走"},{"pid":"760c3802f87590cc324ab1689a5c745851dfa632","tid":2179949,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"口講有咩用 都係睇合約細則"},{"pid":"a3e207c0573eab003e553f4b0dde7847db07a9f3","tid":2179949,"uid":282509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9c3efb49c43fc3f0250ad9e26cd26051454c2547","tid":2179949,"uid":24925,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13: